FT  18 MAR 92 / UK Company News: R&amp;M American Capital assets up
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Net asset values per capital and income share of River &amp; Mercantile American
Capital &amp; Income Trust stood at 37.27p and 65.64p respectively at
end-February.
The figures compared with 30.05p and 61.21p a year earlier.
Available income for the 12 months rose to Pounds 605,000 (Pounds 583,000),
equal to earnings per income share of 8.07p (7.77p). A proposed final
dividend of 2.4p makes a same-again 7.8p total.
