FT  18 MAR 92 / UK Company News: Losses of Pounds 1.06m at Celestion
Industries
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Celestion Industries, a maker of clothes and electronic consumer goods and a
supplier to Marks and Spencer, reported a pre-tax loss of Pounds 1.06m for
