<TEXT>
Terry Fields, who was expelled from the Labour party for his links with
Militant Tendency but is defending Liverpool Broadgreen as an independent,
has found a new way of achieving publicity.
Fields has diverted the permissible costs of producing election leaflets
into making a video, which will be premiered tomorrow evening. He has had
