FT  18 MAR 92 / Election '92: Lib Dems challenge shadow Budget
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
LABOUR has failed to explain whether its shadow Budget includes the Pounds
11bn of privatisation receipts expected by the government, the Liberal
Democrats said yesterday. Mr Alan Beith, Liberal Democrat treasury
spokesman, said that either Labour policy had changed or there was a hole in
its accounts.
