</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Cyrus Vance, the UN special envoy flew to Azerbaijan yesterday to try to
find a way to end the republic's bloody conflict with Armenia over the
disputed territory of Nagorno-Karabakh, Reuter reports from Baku,
Azerbaijan. More than 1,500 people have died in four years of fighting over
