 ------------------------------------------------------
                     Turnover       Trading profit
                   1991    1990   1991         1990
 ------------------------------------------------------
Homes             585.4   658.0   26.2         51.7
Contracting       777.2   917.0   11.2          3.2
Minerals          290.6   297.9   17.4         26.3
Property           40.4    54.0    4.5         18.0
Technology/other   59.6    50.1    0.1         -1.6
Total           1,753.2 1,977.0   59.4         97.6
