poised to take a stake in CKD, Czechoslovakia's biggest transport and
engineering company, for a joint venture making transport vehicles. AEG
intends to diversify CKD's production capacity of 1,200 tramcars and 550
locomotives a year, focusing on making subway cars and suburban trains.
