Costa Rica   9.3
Honduras     8.1
Martinique   7.2
Guadeloupe   4.6
Belize       4.0
St. Lucia    3.8
Ivory Coast  3.7
Cameroon     2.1
Dominica     2.0
Gautemala    1.8
Somalia      1.6
St. Vincent  1.6
Suriname     1.4
